#new:String $ToadGirlTattle
{
[Style Tattle]
That's T. Sune.[BR]
She's a pretty popular singer[BR]
around these parts of[BR]
[SaveColor][Color:07]Starfall Hill[RestoreColor]...[Pause 20] apparently.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I dunno, I've never seen her[BR]
before.[BR]
[Pause 10]But I will say...[BR]
[Wait][Next]
She's pretty freaking cute.[BR]
[Pause 8]I should definitely ask her[BR]
out and get her to sing some[BR]
songs for me.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
That'd really get good old[BR]
Goombarius rolling.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#new:String $ToadBoyTattle
{
[Style Tattle]
That's Shann T.[BR]
[Pause 8]He really admires T. Sune.[BR]
[Pause 8]That rascal! Trying to hog her[BR]
all to himself![BR]
[Wait][Next]
[PrintRising]Who the heck does he think he is?[/fx][BR]
[Pause 5]I had my eye on her first.....[BR]
[Pause 15]not.... [Pause 15]but that still doesn't mean[BR]
I'ma lose to competition like him.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Back me up here, Mario.[BR]
[Pause 5][Wave]C'mon! I'm your best friend.[/fx][BR]
[Wait][End]
}


#new:String $GoombaTattle
{
[Style Tattle]
That's Goomuke.[BR]
[Pause 10]And before you ask, no, it's[BR]
pronounced "Goom-kay".[BR]
[Wait][Next]
This is an oriental district.[BR]
Don't go saying stupid things,[BR]
Mario.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
My boy is just trying to live[BR]
the life and enjoy a nice stay[BR]
with his homie Koopa here.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
After all, the Goombas and[BR]
Koopas are meant to get[BR]
along with each other.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Don't you remember Jeff the[BR]
Goomba and Hal the Koopa? [BR]
Those guys are awesome.[BR]
[Wait][End]
}


#new:String $KoopaTattle
{
[Style Tattle]
That's Koohid.[BR]
He's hanging out in front of[BR]
this oriental-style hotel[BR]
with his buddy Goomba there.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
